Package: InctoolsJulia
Type: Package
Title: R Interface to Inctools.jl - HIV Incidence Estimation Tools (Julia Backend)
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Eduard", "Grebe", email = "eduard@grebe.consulting", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = "Also: egrebe@vitalant.org"),
    person("Claude", "AI", role = "ctb", comment = "R wrapper implementation")
    )
Description: Provides an R interface to the Inctools.jl Julia package for
    estimating HIV incidence using cross-sectional survey data with recency
    biomarkers. Implements the Kassanjee method for incidence estimation with
    support for bootstrap and Delta method uncertainty estimation. This package
    wraps the high-performance Julia implementation and is distinct from the
    'inctools' R package on CRAN. Requires Julia to be installed on the system.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    JuliaCall (>= 0.17.0)
SystemRequirements: Julia (>= 1.6)
RoxygenNote: 7.0.0
URL: https://github.com/SACEMA/inctools
BugReports: https://github.com/SACEMA/inctools/issues
